                  <tgroup align="justify" cols="1">
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="100.00*"/>
                    <tbody>
                      <row quote="1">
                        <entry colsep="0" quote="1" rowsep="0"><emphasis style="italic">English form</emphasis><brk/>I, [<emphasis style="italic">name</emphasis>], swear that I will faithfully and diligently serve Her (<emphasis style="italic">or</emphasis> His) Majesty [<emphasis style="italic">specify the name of the reigning Sovereign, as in:</emphasis> Queen Elizabeth the Second], Queen (<emphasis style="italic">or</emphasis> King) of New Zealand, her (<emphasis style="italic">or</emphasis> his) heirs and successors, as a special constable at [<emphasis style="italic">place</emphasis>], without favour or affection, malice or ill will. While I hold this office I will, to the best of my power, keep the peace and prevent offences against the peace and will, to the best of my skill and knowledge, perform all the duties of the office of special constable according to law. So help me God.</entry>
